26#ifndef _SYS_METASLAB_H
27#define _SYS_METASLAB_H
28
29#include <sys/spa.h>
30#include <sys/space_map.h>
31#include <sys/txg.h>
32#include <sys/zio.h>
33#include <sys/avl.h>
34
35#ifdef __cplusplus
36extern "C" {
37#endif
38
39
40typedef struct metaslab_ops {
41 uint64_t (*msop_alloc)(metaslab_t *, uint64_t);
42} metaslab_ops_t;
43
44
45extern metaslab_ops_t *zfs_metaslab_ops;
46
47int metaslab_init(metaslab_group_t *, uint64_t, uint64_t, uint64_t,
48 metaslab_t **);
49void metaslab_fini(metaslab_t *);
50
51void metaslab_load_wait(metaslab_t *);
52int metaslab_load(metaslab_t *);
53void metaslab_unload(metaslab_t *);
54
55void metaslab_sync(metaslab_t *, uint64_t);
56void metaslab_sync_done(metaslab_t *, uint64_t);
57void metaslab_sync_reassess(metaslab_group_t *);
58uint64_t metaslab_block_maxsize(metaslab_t *);
59
60#define METASLAB_HINTBP_FAVOR 0x0
61#define METASLAB_HINTBP_AVOID 0x1
62#define METASLAB_GANG_HEADER 0x2
63#define METASLAB_GANG_CHILD 0x4
64#define METASLAB_ASYNC_ALLOC 0x8
65#define METASLAB_DONT_THROTTLE 0x10
66
67int metaslab_alloc(spa_t *, metaslab_class_t *, uint64_t,
68 blkptr_t *, int, uint64_t, blkptr_t *, int, zio_alloc_list_t *, zio_t *);
69void metaslab_free(spa_t *, const blkptr_t *, uint64_t, boolean_t);
70int metaslab_claim(spa_t *, const blkptr_t *, uint64_t);
71void metaslab_check_free(spa_t *, const blkptr_t *);
72
73void metaslab_alloc_trace_init(void);
74void metaslab_alloc_trace_fini(void);
75void metaslab_trace_init(zio_alloc_list_t *);
76void metaslab_trace_fini(zio_alloc_list_t *);
77
78metaslab_class_t *metaslab_class_create(spa_t *, metaslab_ops_t *);
79void metaslab_class_destroy(metaslab_class_t *);
80int metaslab_class_validate(metaslab_class_t *);
81void metaslab_class_histogram_verify(metaslab_class_t *);
82uint64_t metaslab_class_fragmentation(metaslab_class_t *);
83uint64_t metaslab_class_expandable_space(metaslab_class_t *);
84boolean_t metaslab_class_throttle_reserve(metaslab_class_t *, int,
85 zio_t *, int);
86void metaslab_class_throttle_unreserve(metaslab_class_t *, int, zio_t *);
87
88void metaslab_class_space_update(metaslab_class_t *, int64_t, int64_t,
89 int64_t, int64_t);
90uint64_t metaslab_class_get_alloc(metaslab_class_t *);
91uint64_t metaslab_class_get_space(metaslab_class_t *);
92uint64_t metaslab_class_get_dspace(metaslab_class_t *);
93uint64_t metaslab_class_get_deferred(metaslab_class_t *);
94uint64_t metaslab_class_get_minblocksize(metaslab_class_t *mc);
95
96metaslab_group_t *metaslab_group_create(metaslab_class_t *, vdev_t *);
97void metaslab_group_destroy(metaslab_group_t *);
98void metaslab_group_activate(metaslab_group_t *);
99void metaslab_group_passivate(metaslab_group_t *);
100boolean_t metaslab_group_initialized(metaslab_group_t *);
101uint64_t metaslab_group_get_space(metaslab_group_t *);
102void metaslab_group_histogram_verify(metaslab_group_t *);
103uint64_t metaslab_group_fragmentation(metaslab_group_t *);
104void metaslab_group_histogram_remove(metaslab_group_t *, metaslab_t *);
105void metaslab_group_alloc_decrement(spa_t *, uint64_t, void *, int);
106void metaslab_group_alloc_verify(spa_t *, const blkptr_t *, void *);

109}
